Package org.activebpel.rt.xml.schema

Interface Summary
IAeComplexTypeFilter interface for filtering complex types
IAeElementFilter interface for filtering elements
IAeSchemaType An interface that all schema type classes should implement.
IAeSchemaTypeVisitor Visitor interface for schema types.
IAeTypeMapper Interface which all type mappers should adhere to.
